{
  "stem": "14060.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I can draw you a picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In 1965, I drive up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I want to show my wife, who was alone born in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And at the age of two, her parents escaped from Austria and went to Belgium and then to Australia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I say look, this is the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We used to have an apartment on this floor-- tall, sort of Austrian-style holiday resort-- flat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And this is where we used to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "While I was there, I speak to the person in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This time, it was already a pensione, you know, where they let rooms, not flats anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remembered that my father, in 1937, as we got into the fiacre-- you know, that is the horse-drawn sort of carriage which we went to the station with-- that we don't know whether we would be able to come back here next year; it was in the summer of '37-- because the owners have got already a swastika flag.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in '65 when I am there, I go in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I speak the language, no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, in good German, [SPEAKING GERMAN], Who are the owners?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, she says-- because I said, as a child, I used to come here on holiday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't say when or what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she says oh, yes, they are the same people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They live in Graz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Graz is [LAUGHS] in the southern part of Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It is like all other parts of-- [LAUGHS] most other parts of Austria, it's a hotbed of Nazism.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And just to show you, nothing has changed as far as they are concerned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the government is trying to say whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
